{"tid":578260,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Galaxy S9 僅可連續拍攝 5 分鐘4K60fps","createTime":"2018-03-02T12:52:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-04T16:21:55.000Z","uid":1130,"like":38,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"69ad04796af645e9a0a7e6f9ba99542286cce3ce","tid":578260,"uid":1130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T12:52:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.newmobilelife.com/2018/03/02/galaxy-s9-4k-video/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newmobilelife.com%2F2018%2F03%2F02%2Fgalaxy-s9-4k-video%2F&d=eY5UXxbvZ0WcAG%2BJmA8FFr%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=b5a6e8fe\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.newmobilelife.com/2018/03/02/galaxy-s9-4k-video/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.loli.net/2018/03/02/5a9948f80f006.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.loli.net%2F2018%2F03%2F02%2F5a9948f80f006.jpeg&h=0d1bfee5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nDxOMark 最新報告顯示，Galaxy S9 Plus 以 104 分奪得最強手機鏡頭稱號，超越 iPhone X。除此之外 Galaxy S9 還支持 4K + 60fps 拍攝，不過有用戶則發現，Galaxy S9 的 4K + 60fps 影片拍攝有一個限制，而且不限於 Exynos 9810 以及驍龍 845 版本，<span style=\"color: red;\">就是僅可連續拍攝 5 分鐘的 4K + 60fps 影片。</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而主要原因是因為當手機開啟 4K + 60fps 影片拍攝模式的時候，會運用大量記憶體以及處理器，因此會導致手機溫度急升，而設定 5 分鐘會減輕手機的負荷。<br />\n<br />\n值得一提的是 iPhone X 的 4K + 60fps 影片拍攝沒有時間的限制，唯一的限制就是視乎 iPhone X 的存儲空間夠不夠。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n延伸閱讀:<a href=\"https://www.notebookcheck.net/Samsung-Galaxy-S9-vs-Sony-Xperia-XZ2-Overview-of-the-differences-in-terms-of-video-recording-HDR-4K-Super-SloMo.287174.0.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.notebookcheck.net%2FSamsung-Galaxy-S9-vs-Sony-Xperia-XZ2-Overview-of-the-differences-in-terms-of-video-recording-HDR-4K-Super-SloMo.287174.0.html&d=eY5UXxbvZ0WcAG%2BJmA8FFr%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=5ba1c06e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.notebookcheck.net/Samsung-Galaxy-S9-vs-Sony-Xperia-XZ2-Overview-of-the-differences-in-terms-of-video-recording-HDR-4K-Super-SloMo.287174.0.html</a>"},{"pid":"f4736474e6d5c2218816e55a5fa31d9b7447c05e","tid":578260,"uid":609,"like":72,"dislike":4,"score":68,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T13:08:25.000Z","msg":"Shamesung: 用家問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外香港人真係善忘 note7全球回收但唔包括香港呢單咁快就忘得一乾二淨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 俾人當狗咁撚完一鑊 轉個頭又烚熟狗頭咁搶住買s8 note8<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  冇d骨氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf3fc0366abc7823dac28e90f9d540dafa9d24a1","tid":578260,"uid":10717,"like":6,"dislike":6,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T13:09:12.000Z","msg":"Xzp 4k可以拍到無電<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90ce8254a6a9e03a82eeff8f9ed8984f6dda9836","tid":578260,"uid":37688,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T13:16:13.000Z","msg":"即係粒高通廢定exynos廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17afc3505ae7048e5a7a3cbca5609e6eb71fdb5f","tid":578260,"uid":15835,"like":13,"dislike":6,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T13:19:25.000Z","msg":"iPhone 贏粒 U 就夠晒 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7b1ebf6fa6468854ff6b8cae66112a026817006","tid":578260,"uid":22553,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"90ce8254a6a9e03a82eeff8f9ed8984f6dda9836","tid":578260,"uid":37688,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T13:16:13.000Z","msg":"即係粒高通廢定exynos廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-02T13:19:43.000Z","msg":"上面又話xzp可以拍到無電，即係唔關u事？"},{"pid":"fc3b4913dafd1011fee27cdb541669b3c4e2ecc7","tid":578260,"uid":37688,"like":1